OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud
OL,6,Fbreaking up a little during the
OL,7,Fevening to bring some late sunshine.
OL,8,FThicker cloud in the north tonight
OL,9,Fwith the odd spot of rain. Mild with
OL,10,Flight winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FEarly showers easing then a
OL,13,Fdry day with bright spells of
OL,14,Fsunshine. Turning cloudier into the
OL,15,Fafternoon with low cloud arriving
OL,16,Falong the south coasts. Feeling warm
OL,17,Fin the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
